==Gothic==
===Etymology===
From Proto-Germanic '''[[*wulfaz]]''' < Proto-Indo-European '''[[*wlqwos]]/[[*lukwos]]''', < Proto-Indo-European base '''[[*wlp-]]/[[*lup-]]'''. Cognates include Sanskrit ''[[vrkas]]'', Lithuanian ''[[vilkas]]'', Russian ''[[ﾐｲﾐｾﾐｻﾐｺ]]'', Albanian ''[[ulk]]'', Latin ''[[vulpes]]'', English ''[[wolf]]'', German ''[[Wolf]]'', and probably Greek [[ﾎｻﾏ歳ｺﾎｿﾏ﹅] and Latin [[lupus]].


